        "type": "translatable",
        "translate": "phenom.dialog.help.recipes.shields.description",
        "fallback": "Besides wooden ones, you can now craft stone, copper, iron, golden, diamond, and netherite shields. Each shield differs in durability and cooldown time after heavy hits (mob with axe, warden)."
