        "type": "translatable",
        "translate": "phenom.dialog.help.recipes.shields.stone.crafting",
        "fallback": "To craft a stone shield, replace all planks in the wooden shield recipe with cobblestone (cobbled deepslate and blackstone also work)."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "minecraft:plain_message",
      "width": 300,
      "contents": {
        "type": "translatable",
        "translate": "phenom.dialog.help.recipes.shields.metal.crafting",
        "fallback": "To craft a copper/iron/golden/diamond shield, replace all planks in the wooden shield recipe with copper/iron/gold ingots or diamond respectively, and the iron ingot with a copper/iron/gold/diamond block respectively."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "minecraft:plain_message",
